data.description: Take a look at this lovely 4 bedroom home located on Arland Place in Montesano, AKA Candy Cane Lane! This place feels like home with 3 large bedrooms & a full bath w/jetted tub on the main floor and the master bedroom & 3/4 bath on the upper floor. There is a charming balcony accessed from the master bedroom that overlooks the private, fully fenced back yard. There is a breakfast bar in the large kitchen and a natural gas free standing stove in the over sized family room to keep things cozy.
data.whatILove: This home is located in a great Montesano neighborhood (AKA Candycane Lane)!
